Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,On the voyage to their next destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and crew drop by\Nthe resort ship, Spa Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,While enjoying their vacation,\Nthey meet the sisters Sayo and Rina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ocean raccoon dog, Nukki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doomed now that\NI've run into you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Foxy and his goons are after it, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This notebook explains how to create jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please help--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and crew managed\Nto repel the Foxy Crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which was after the sisters' notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It held the secret to their father's\Nresearch on making jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But now Sayo has been taken hostage\Nby the mastermind, Doran!
