Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang! This ship is loaded with traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pathetic, "Silver Fox" Foxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They won despite your trickery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. Now I simply have to wait for\Nthem to solve the secret of the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This just isn't enough to go by!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you search all over the ship?\NWasn't there a large "X" mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No... What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This notebook really is full of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And now my sister is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--Luffy!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save... Big Sis Sayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're sure? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wanna see those jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though this notebook could be lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But how are we going to save her, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Why don't we destroy this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, man! Are you thinking straight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Sayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find her if we destroy the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And the hint about the jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be easier to look for if we destroy the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no point worrying about something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nthat might not be on this ship, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, you guys don't\Nhave a shred of delicacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san, the idea of meekly obeying
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nthat dastardly mustache irks me to no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if we sink this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! Not you too, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't someone going to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were the Captain's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're quick on the uptake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look after Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There goes the resort...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Destroy this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,108-Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Concasser!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabasco Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoofprint Roseo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunderbolt Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Clutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-Verse Humming... Nock Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Sayo back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta my way! Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Like those puny bullets can hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He repelled the bullets?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Owie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerks! Now I'm ticked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come on and give Sayo back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a cannon?! I thought it was a chimney!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! He's taken her hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you wreak havoc on my ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize how much\Nit cost to build Spa Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that rotten mustached jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Next I'm gonna blow that brat sky high!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I had originally wanted you to\Nsolve the puzzle in that notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but forget it! I'll be taking that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give her back after you hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have the notebook,\Nso give Big Sis Sayo back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Sayo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:10:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rina, solve the secret in the notebook\Nand finish Dad's research!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in Dad, Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give Dad's research to that jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad was working to make his
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,dream come true for you, me, and everyone in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! For my sake,\Ndon't throw away Dad's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying! Dad is just\Na self-absorbed researcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rina...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... I mean, he was\Nalways in his own world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:40.11,"Sign",,0,0,0,,{\fad(443,0)}"For Dad"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's done!\N--It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Dad will like his birthday cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he must have found something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:31.50,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"For Dad"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A cake? Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have baked a cake for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cast-off Thirty Year Cicada shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,\NI can probably use them in my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a big outbreak of them\Nfor the first time in thirty years!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? Ah! But last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A cake! That cake looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But that cake...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We made that yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have gone bad. It is summer and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor... Get a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He already saw you and left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about him!\NHe doesn't know a thing about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't think about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this isn't the time to get in a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't butt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rina, you're mistaken! Listen to me! Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking forward to having\Na birthday party, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the materials in the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,cast-off Thirty Year Cicada shells to make the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't get them now, I'd have\Nto wait another thirty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. But I bet Rina is mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You are just like your mother,\Nbut Rina takes after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a handful when she gets upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,After I make some jewels,\Nlet's eat a cake that's this big!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get one that Rina could hide in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nukki says that it's all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And he said that your father\Nleft home to protect you and Sayo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,from some bad guys who\Nwere after his jewel research.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to work to find a four-leaf clover.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But Big Sis found three of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because she believed with all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nof her heart that she would find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--She believed?\N--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Conducting research and searching\Nfor four-leaf clovers are similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you never stop believing and work hard,\Nit will pay off in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Then I'm going to find a five-leaf clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Five leaves...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a five-leaf clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's... Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right! I believed I could find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Rina! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Rina! I'm gonna\Nsucceed with my research!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I had forgotten all about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to believe he could pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Dad's dream! It has to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've changed my mind! You can't\Nhave the notebook after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's show time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play games with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Seis Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabasco Star Onslaught! Star! Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami, get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Untie her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A lock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...Great Buddha Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're doing a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you need to do a great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The jerk! He released all\Nof the steam in the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gear 3:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bone Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gigant Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! Don't forget about\Neveryone who has to abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops! I forgot that I shrink\Nwhen I use that move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:18:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh! Think ahead a little, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A giant "X."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves the jerk right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,An "X"! And it's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Dad was referring to that\Nunderwater volcano on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doran built his ship right above\Nthe treasure he was searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The doof didn't realize the key\Nto the secret was right under him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... a circular rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a round rainbow before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mysterious rainbow! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a sec! Is that the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, circular rainbows\Nare referred to as the "ocean's treasure."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not tell me that this is the treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have all of the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give us that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That rainbow looks weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The order of the colors is inversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The order...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"-Several Days Later-"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the monster raccoon dog\Nfrom the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's an ocean raccoon dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Sayo-chan's guess\Nwas dead on back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Luffy and friends. Are you well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My big sister and I went straight\Nhome and tested out her idea."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We followed my father's formulas\Nand made seven different medications.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When we mixed them together in\Nthe order of the circular rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.66,0:22:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She says it created a jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayo... Rina...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.43,0:22:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.92,0:22:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a sign of their gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, "Thank you, guys."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get a better look at it, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,--I wanna see it! Lemme see!\N--Huh? Let's see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! This isn't a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.92,0:23:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's candy rain! Ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.68,0:23:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. I dropped the jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--Which one is it?!\N--Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Find it! Find it fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys had better find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.99,0:23:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so excited, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,After learning about the great feats\Nyou've accomplished on your voyage,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've realized I must work\Nto become a true comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.27,0:23:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"A true comrade"? That's not\Nsomething you work toward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.58,0:23:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.87,0:23:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Brook's Great Struggle\NA Bumpy Road to True Companionship?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
